00:36:37,070 --> 00:36:37,800
Set a time with her.

860
00:36:46,480 --> 00:36:47,070
Come, let's eat.

861
00:36:51,110 --> 00:36:52,150
Don't you also feel

862
00:36:52,670 --> 00:36:53,480
something's missing?

863
00:36:53,760 --> 00:36:54,280
Missing?

864
00:36:55,190 --> 00:36:55,800
Let's drink.

865
00:36:59,070 --> 00:37:00,760
Should've bought more dishes earlier.

866
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:05,630
Come.

867
00:37:06,960 --> 00:37:07,280
Here.

868
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:10,960
Congratulations.

869
00:37:11,480 --> 00:37:12,190
Congratulations to us both.

870
00:37:20,400 --> 00:37:20,800
Mr. Li,

871
00:37:21,110 --> 00:37:23,070
that kid who added me last time

872
00:37:23,070 --> 00:37:24,030
has been contacting me,

873
00:37:24,030 --> 00:37:25,030
asking when to meet.

874
00:37:25,280 --> 00:37:26,030
Some instructions?

875
00:37:28,510 --> 00:37:30,070
Since Mr. Gu referred them,

876
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:31,440
just meet them

877
00:37:32,510 --> 00:37:34,400
But trust business is serious.

878
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:36,400
Will cost lots of money later.

879
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:38,110
As the old saying goes,

880
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:39,630
beardless mouth,

881
00:37:40,110 --> 00:37:41,030
unreliable work.

882
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:42,280
Understood.

883
00:37:42,710 --> 00:37:43,760
So should I meet or will you?

884
00:37:44,150 --> 00:37:44,960
You meet them.

885
00:37:46,150 --> 00:37:46,510
By the way,

886
00:37:46,800 --> 00:37:48,150
Keke called me last week.

887
00:37:48,280 --> 00:37:50,480
Said her favorite singer
is having a concert.

888
00:37:50,590 --> 00:37:51,630
Asked me to buy tickets.

889
00:37:51,960 --> 00:37:52,760
Then just buy them.

890
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:53,630
Why are you asking me?

891
00:37:54,710 --> 00:37:57,630
