892
00:38:01,190 --> 00:38:02,320
Entertainment is entertainment.

893
00:38:02,670 --> 00:38:04,030
Life is life.

894
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:04,800
Understood.

895
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:06,800
Best seats in VIP section.

896
00:38:07,230 --> 00:38:09,960
Also, Keke mustn't know
that you know about this.

897
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:15,710
What if she asks about it?

898
00:38:16,110 --> 00:38:16,920
You're still angry.

899
00:38:16,960 --> 00:38:17,880
Very angry.

900
00:38:17,920 --> 00:38:19,360
She must come to apologize to you.

901
00:38:22,230 --> 00:38:23,550
What if she doesn't ask?

902
00:38:25,230 --> 00:38:26,760
You should tell her proactively!

903
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:27,550
Tell her I'm hospitalized!

904
00:38:27,550 --> 00:38:28,920
I've received critical condition notice!

905
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:31,280
Mr. Li, you shouldn't
curse yourself like this.

906
00:38:33,110 --> 00:38:33,710
How could...

907
00:38:34,760 --> 00:38:36,070
You're not better!

908
00:38:36,670 --> 00:38:37,510
I will curse myself!

909
00:38:39,280 --> 00:38:39,760
Understood.

910
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:41,320
What do you mean "understood"?

911
00:38:41,550 --> 00:38:42,360
Nothing else? Leave!

912
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:43,190
Understood.

913
00:38:45,510 --> 00:38:46,110
Every single day...

914
00:38:46,110 --> 00:38:47,360
Sooner or later I'll be in hospital.

915
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:51,800
How did it end again?

916
00:39:00,440 --> 00:39:00,880
What?

917
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:02,070
No tickets left?

918
00:39:02,320 --> 00:39:03,280
No tickets? Buy them!

919
00:39:03,960 --> 00:39:05,440
You can't even buy concert tickets?

920
00:39:06,030 --> 00:39:06,840
If you can't handle it,

921
00:39:06,840 --> 00:39:07,710
don't come to work tomorrow.

922
00:39:08,880 --> 00:39:09,400
Hello, Ms. Yan.

923
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:10,800
I just ordered you

924
00:39:11,280 --> 00:39:11,760
a latte.

925
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:12,480
Okay, thank you.

926
00:39:13,000 --> 00:39:14,590
I have some urgent messages to reply to.

927
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:17,280
Please go ahead with what you were saying.

928
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:17,670
It won't interfere.

929
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:19,920
Ms. Yan.

930
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:21,400
I'm from TSI,

931
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:22,710
Head of the Family Office.

932
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,710
My name is Xue Xiaozhou.

933
00:39:24,280 --> 00:39:25,510
Our primary clients are

934
00:39:25,510 --> 00:39:26,630
high-net-worth individuals.

935
00:39:26,630 --> 00:39:27,000
[Concert in Shanghai]

936
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:29,480
We handle their family wealth management
and inheritance

937
00:39:30,590 --> 00:39:31,670
Here's our company introduction.

938
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:32,550
Please take a look.

939
00:39:37,590 --> 00:39:38,710
TSI.

940
00:39:39,960 --> 00:39:41,400
So you're
a newly established family office.

941
00:39:41,510 --> 00:39:42,710
Yes, we've just been established,

942
00:39:42,710 --> 00:39:44,190
But all departments in our company

943
00:39:44,190 --> 00:39:44,960
have already allocated most resources

944
00:39:44,960 --> 00:39:45,360
[Chen Xiaotian's concert]

945
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:47,000
towards family office services.

946
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:48,960
As for our family office,

947
00:39:49,070 --> 00:39:50,150
- actually, we have... - Okay.

948
00:39:50,190 --> 00:39:50,760
I understand.

949
00:39:50,760 --> 00:39:52,320
You have your
business introduction here?

950
00:39:52,630 --> 00:39:53,480
The business introduction is right here.

951
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,920
I'll take this back to have a look.

952
00:40:01,710 --> 00:40:02,400
Please review it first then.

953
00:40:02,400 --> 00:40:03,760
We'll schedule another meeting later.

954
00:40:04,590 --> 00:40:04,920
Alright.

955
00:40:05,440 --> 00:40:05,800
Let's meet again.

956
00:40:06,320 --> 00:40:06,920
Ms. Yan.

957
00:40:07,360 --> 00:40:08,880
That concert you mentioned earlier,

958
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:10,760
is it Chen Xiaotian's concert?

959
00:40:11,550 --> 00:40:11,920
Yes.

960
00:40:12,150 --> 00:40:12,550
What's wrong?

961
00:40:13,070 --> 00:40:13,960
I can get tickets.

962
00:40:14,150 --> 00:40:14,880
Are you sure?

963
00:40:15,510 --> 00:40:17,320
It sold out within minutes
after sales opened.

964
00:40:18,150 --> 00:40:18,800
Ms. Yan.

965
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:20,880
We serve high-net-worth individuals.

966
00:40:21,030 --> 00:40:22,960
If we can't even secure concert tickets,

967
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,800
how can we satisfy our clients?

968
00:40:26,070 --> 00:40:28,110
Center seats. Members and scalpers
are all sold out.

969
00:40:28,440 --> 00:40:29,510
No problem, leave it to me.

970
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:31,590
Okay, waiting for your update.

971
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:32,670
Keep in touch.

972
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:44,550
About those tickets,

973
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:45,710
I'll try my best to get them for you.

974
00:40:46,400 --> 00:40:46,840
Wait for my update.

975
00:40:49,190 --> 00:40:50,920
Don't worry, the middleman confirmed

976
00:40:51,550 --> 00:40:52,670
tickets can be obtained, no problem.

977
00:40:58,360 --> 00:40:59,000
What's wrong?

978
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:02,320
You're upset because I got the tickets
and stole your thunder?

979
00:41:02,840 --> 00:41:03,480
Not happy?

980
00:41:04,030 --> 00:41:05,030
That's not why.

981
00:41:05,030 --> 00:41:06,630
Her boss is our major client.

982
00:41:06,630 --> 00:41:07,230
That's correct.

983
00:41:07,230 --> 00:41:08,510
But we're not babysitters either.

984
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:09,960
Today we helped them get tickets.

985
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:10,630
Right?

986
00:41:10,710 --> 00:41:12,510
What if tomorrow
they say their toilet is clogged.

987
00:41:12,510 --> 00:41:13,400
Should we go fix that too?

988
00:41:13,840 --> 00:41:15,000
I'd be overjoyed if

989
00:41:15,840 --> 00:41:17,400
he really asked me
to go fix their toilet.

990
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:19,110
That means they treat me as family.

991
00:41:19,710 --> 00:41:22,030
We shouldn't always
fawn over big clients.

992
00:41:22,030 --> 00:41:23,710
Sometimes refusal is an attitude too.

993
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:24,630
Saying no

994
00:41:24,630 --> 00:41:26,070
shows you've got confidence.

995
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:28,030
Li Fendou is my client.

996
00:41:28,190 --> 00:41:29,070
Let me take the lead, okay?

997
00:41:29,070 --> 00:41:29,960
This time, follow my lead.

998
00:41:31,360 --> 00:41:33,070
That's what I said initially.

999
00:41:34,110 --> 00:41:35,400
But petty officials
are hard to deal with.

1000
00:41:35,670 --> 00:41:37,230
Especially those around the boss.

1001
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:39,760
We don't need their help.

1002
00:41:40,070 --> 00:41:41,840
We just need them not to sabotage us.

1003
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:44,840
Just leave this person to me.

1004
00:41:45,000 --> 00:41:46,230
I'll handle it for you, alright?

1005
00:41:46,760 --> 00:41:48,070
When you finally meet Li Fendou,

1006
00:41:48,070 --> 00:41:49,480
I won't interfere anymore, okay?

1007
00:41:51,280 --> 00:41:52,190
About those concert tickets,

1008
00:41:52,550 --> 00:41:54,320
I've already paid the middleman.

1009
00:41:54,510 --> 00:41:55,110
If we don't take the tickets,

1010
00:41:55,590 --> 00:41:56,960
the money's wasted.

1011
00:41:58,710 --> 00:41:59,840
Won't let it happen again, okay?

1012
00:42:00,110 --> 00:42:00,590
Okay.

1013
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:01,190
Fine then.

1014
00:42:15,190 --> 00:42:17,030
It's been almost an hour now.

1015
00:42:17,320 --> 00:42:18,840
Ms. Yan still hasn't shown up.

1016
00:42:19,800 --> 00:42:20,630
You did contact her, right?

1017
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:22,480
Yes, I texted her when I arrived.

1018
00:42:22,480 --> 00:42:23,070
No reply though.

1019
00:42:23,710 --> 00:42:24,360
And this appointment time

1020
00:42:24,360 --> 00:42:25,800
was set by herself three days ago,

1021
00:42:26,800 --> 00:42:28,000
That shouldn't happen.

1022
00:42:29,400 --> 00:42:30,670
If something came up suddenly,

1023
00:42:31,230 --> 00:42:32,550
she should have notified us earlier.

1024
00:42:35,000 --> 00:42:36,360
Now leaving us hanging here

1025
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:38,400
isn't a good sign.

1026
00:42:43,110 --> 00:42:44,110
Let me call her.

1027
00:42:47,630 --> 00:42:49,550
Ms. Yan, thanks for today.

1028
00:42:49,760 --> 00:42:50,280
Don't mention it.

1029
00:42:50,840 --> 00:42:52,320
We'll leave the rest to you.

